```plantuml
@startuml BoraxTheClean_DevelopmentMachine

actor Developer
participant "GitHub Actions" as GitHub
participant "AWS CloudFormation" as CF
participant "AWS EC2" as EC2
participant "AWS IAM" as IAM
participant "AWS CloudWatch" as CW

Developer -> GitHub: Push Code
GitHub -> GitHub: Trigger Workflow
GitHub -> CF: Deploy CloudFormation Stack

CF -> IAM: Create IAM Role with Admin Access
CF -> EC2: Launch EC2 Instance with IAM Profile
CF -> EC2: Configure Security Group (SSH Access)

note over EC2: EC2 Instance is running

Developer -> EC2: SSH Access
EC2 -> IAM: Validate IAM Role
EC2 -> CW: Monitor Inactivity

alt Inactive for 1 hour
  CW -> EC2: Trigger Shutdown
  note over EC2: EC2 Instance is stopped
end

@enduml
```